com.google.gcloud.datastore

Class PartialEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.datastore.PartialEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Entity

    public class PartialEntity
extends Object
    A partial entity holds one or more properties, represented by a name (as String) and a value (as Value). For a list of possible values see Value.Type. A partial entity also can be associated with a key (partial or full). This class is immutable.
